textBeforeTable: Engine Power Thrust models are available in 25" as well. Available in 15 and 20 inch shaft lengths A integrated carrying handle makes transporting the engine a breeze. The convenient, foldaway carry handle is situated at the exact top/bottom balance point of the engine. This means the engine carries more easily in a level position. Integrated Carrying Handle - easier transport Conveniently allows user to tilt the unit out of the water. At low speeds acts like a power shallow-water-drive device, permitting access to the shallow water areas. Power Tilt Conventional 2-circuit carburetors go directly from a lean mixture at idle to a rich setting at full throttle. The BF15 and 20 add a third stage for better economy and smoother operation. 3 Stage Carburetion - better fuel economy
